name: compiler_deep_v8_array_head_inside_with_after_set
section: runtime-arrays-v8
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Array head in a mutable environment should be stable across unrelated mutation.
law: (= (with [xs [{a} {b}] x {b}] (do (when {p} (set! x {a})) (head xs))) {a})
